анию).\n - Дом находится на охраняемой территории.\n\n - Квартиру представляет агент Capital Mars - Ирина.\n - ID объекта 355967.", "photos": [{"id": 2396548537, "isDefault": false, "fullUrl": "https://images.cdn-cian.ru/images/2396548537-1.jpg", "thumbnailUrl": "https://images.cdn-cian.ru/images/2396548537-2.jpg", "thumbnail2Url": "https://images.cdn-cian.ru/images/2396548537-4.jpg", "miniUrl": "https://images.cdn-cian.ru/images/2396548537-3.jpg", "isLayout": false, "isCianLayout": false}, {"id": 2396548580, "isDefault": false, "fullUrl": "https://images.cdn-cian.ru/images/2396548580-1.jpg", "thumbnailUrl": "https://images.cdn-cian.ru/images/2396548580-2.jpg", "thumbnail2Url": "https://images.cdn-cian.ru/images/2396548580-4.jpg", "miniUrl": "https://images.cdn-cian.ru/images/2396548580-3.jpg", "isLayout": false, "isCianLayout": false}, {"id": 2396548590, "isDefault": false, "fullUrl": "https://images.cdn-cian.ru/images/2396548590-1.jpg", "thumbnailUrl": "https://images.cdn-cian.ru/images/2396548590-2.jpg", "thumbnail2Url": "https://images.cdn-cian.ru/images/2396548590-4.jpg", "miniUrl": "https://images.cdn-cian.ru/images/2396548590-3.jpg", "isLayout": true, "isCianLayout": false}, {"id": 2396548616, "isDefault": false, "fullUrl": "https://images.cdn-cian.ru/images/2396548616-1.jpg", "thumbnailUrl": "https://images.cdn-cian.ru/images/2396548616-2.jpg", "thumbnail2Url": "https://images.cdn-cian.ru/images/2396548616-4.jpg", "miniUrl": "https://images.cdn-cian.ru/images/2396548616-3.jpg", "isLayout": false, "isCianLayout": false}, {"id": 2396548666, "isDefault": false, "fullUrl": "https://images.cdn-cian.ru/images/2396548666-1.jpg", "thumbnailUrl": "https://images.cdn-cian.ru/images/2396548666-2.jpg", "thumbnail2Url": "https://images.cdn-cian.ru/images/2396548666-4.jpg", "miniUrl": "https://images.cdn-cian.ru/images/2396548666-3.jpg", "isLayout": false, "isCianLayout": false}, {"id": 2396548723, "isDefault": false, "fullUrl": "https://images.cdn-cian.ru/images/23965487